  'My boyfriend specifically asked me what I think I bring to the table in a relationship. That automatically makes me think that he doesn''t feel like I am doing the things that a woman should do or that he''s not happy. It really comes down to this recurring argument that we always have about him being jealous that I am still friends with my ex-boyfriend even though I haven''t been with my ex-boyfriend in over six years. He wants me to completely cut off communication with Chris, who''s my ex, but that goes against all of my values and integrity. I can''t just cut someone out of my life for no reason.',
