- Corona Beers
- Tequila Shots

Party Details:
👉 *TOMORROW*, Saturday, October 19th | 6–11 PM
👉 *Location*: The Grand, Townhouse 7, Dubai Creek Harbour (Google Maps)
❤️‍🔥 Music, champagne, drinks, and delicious food
🍾 Dancefloor, big terrace, and rooftop – plenty of space to party!
😎 Stunning views from the terrace and rooftop: Burj Khalifa, Downtown Skyline, and the Creek

*CHARITY*
The theme of the night is to help me build a school in Morocco. I’m not asking anyone to bring anything or cover costs – I only ask for a generous donation to support the school project. Every bit helps!

Learn more about the cause and my story here 👉 https://gofund.me/7ac6274d

*HOW TO GET THERE*
I live in the *Townhouse 7* in “_The Grand_” building in _Dubai Creek Harbour_ (Ras Al Khor). Please note that the security at the reception can be a bit tricky, so here’s how to make it smoother:
🔹 For an easier route, enter through the parking and walk straight until you see the “Townhouses” sign. I’ll share a photo in the group to help.
🔹 Alternatively, you can go to the reception and ask for Townhouse 7 – but this might take longer, so I recommend going through the parking!

*AFTER PARTY*
We’ll wrap up the house party around 11 PM, but the night doesn’t end there! I’ve reserved two tables at Iris nightclub for the after-party.
👉 Total minimum spend for both tables together will be 25K AED (~7K USD), and consumption at the club will be on everyone individually.
I’ll post a poll in the group – if we have enough people (around 20), we’ll keep the reservation.

*Bringing Guests*
Feel free to bring guests, but please ensure they align with our values, respect our privacy, and share in our generosity for the charity cause.

Can’t wait to party with all of you tomorrow! Let’s make it a night to remember.

Bless,
Levin',
